    "Details": "One of the first mass production QuadMechs, the 55 ton Scorpion entered production in 2570 as an infantry support unit. Shunned by most MechWarriors due to its notoriously unstable gait, the Scorpion would nevertheless see uninterrupted use throughout the Succession Wars and beyond. The Scorpion 1BR is powered by a 330-rated Light Fusion Engine giving it a top speed of 97 km/h. An ER PPC and a Streak SRM-6 form the Mechs weapons load. MASC provides improved speed for short periods.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Lifesupport</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
